  "body": "For the following snippet of code:\n\n```\nvar A = React.createClass({\n    childContextTypes: {\n        x: React.PropTypes.string\n    },\n    getChildContext: function() {\n        return {x: '42'};\n    },\n    render: function() {\n        if (this.props.children) {\n            return <div>props.children: {this.props.children}</div>\n        } else {\n            return <div>regular: <B/></div>;\n        }\n    }\n});\n\nvar B = React.createClass({\n    contextTypes: {\n        x: React.PropTypes.string\n    },\n    render: function() {\n        return <span>X = {this.context.x}</span>;\n    }\n});\n\nReact.renderComponent(\n    <div>\n        <A />\n        <A><B/></A>\n    </div>,\n\n    document.body\n);\n```\n\nThe output will be:\n\n```\nregular: X = 42\nprops.children: X =\n```\n",
